A survey on neutrality of mass media was conducted titled Facts Affecting Trust in News Media Among Young People in Bangladesh. One of the questions was whether medias and news reporters collect news neutrally. The results are shown below. 

Opinion Media Reporter
Strongly Agree 25.3 28.1
Disagree 49.3 40.2
No Comments 14.0 19.5
Agree 11.4 12.1

News captures the whole picture

